  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">We present in this note a lower bound for the Calabi functional in a given Kähler class. This yields an integral inequality for constant scalar curvature metrics, which can be viewed as a refinement of S.-T. Yau's Chern number inequality from the Einstein metric case to constant scalar curvature metric case.</subfield>
